Class JsonCollectionsAutoConfiguration

java.lang.Object
com.oracle.spring.json.JsonCollectionsAutoConfiguration
@AutoConfiguration public class JsonCollectionsAutoConfiguration extends Object
Autoconfiguration for the JSON Collections beans. OKafka-related beans are only instantiated if the required interfaces are on the classpath.
